{"tid":941124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 牛頭角劍橋長者疑遭塞肛亡","createTime":"2018-12-14T13:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T15:16:43.000Z","uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"29af0a5dd7c2d11184d2e577a01280adbc39fadc","tid":941124,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:37:59.000Z","msg":"該宗懷疑虐老個案發生於2016年1月。申訴專員公署指出，涉事院友因低血壓及排黑糞便，被送往醫院後，驗出其肛門有布塊和尿片膠紙，疑涉虐老，家人報警，但院友2日後去世，現時個案仍待死因裁判法庭指示。<br />\n<br />\n公署指出，事發後社署派員巡查，發現涉事院舍一周內4天人手不足，但沒按既定程序在7個工作天發出警告信，拖延5個多月才發出；社署又發現該院提供虛假的值勤記錄，也沒作深入調查，更未按法例予以檢控。公署批評社署跟進懷疑虐老個案不夠積極。本報翻查資料，一名入住牛頭角定業街劍橋護老院的60歲智障男院友，2016年1月31日因肺炎入院，被醫護人員發現其肛門及腸道深處塞有紗布、尿片膠貼等異物，家屬懷疑虐老報警求助，男院友兩日後去世。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181214/20568400\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181214%2F20568400&d=naVV2UsrwoB%2BRHXBd48YuZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=cf53f846\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181214%2F20568400&h=2dc60521\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181214/20568400</a>"},{"pid":"a3d7fee48305dc7718520e23329a581655e92fb6","tid":941124,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:38:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796ddc48b2ef1d5fabdd9520472444c7f1a8b57f","tid":941124,"uid":90,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:40:56.000Z","msg":"老貓未來"},{"pid":"d40c1643c4da3be27c2310817e38e26cfd1d282f","tid":941124,"uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"796ddc48b2ef1d5fabdd9520472444c7f1a8b57f","tid":941124,"uid":90,"